keyFacts: Verizon responded to a subpoena (Case #19143314) for telephone records covering July 6, 2019 to August 13, 2019.
The legal compliance note states 'NO CALLS FOUND ON THE BILL' for certain periods/locations, suggesting limited activity.
Two specific calls are recorded: one from NJ to NY on July 10, 2019, and one from NJ to Anaheim, CA on July 13, 2019.
The document is part of a larger investigation, as indicated by the case number and references to Verizon Security Assistance Team.
The billing date shown is July 24, 2019, which corresponds to the period being investigated.
